<li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India&#x27;s Education Paradox: Rising Enrolment, Falling Learning — What Went Wrong?</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->Income Inequality in India: The Top 1% Now Owns 40% of the Wealth</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-China at the Crossroads: Four Years After Galwan, the Border Remains the Flashpoint</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India&#x27;s Foreign Policy at 80: From Non-Alignment to Multi-Alignment</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->The Satluj Files: Censored, Released, Removed — The 48-Hour Life of India&#x27;s Most Controversial Film</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-US Relations: From Nuclear Deal to Critical Technology Partnership</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-Indonesia: How Maritime Neighbours Are Reshaping the Indo-Pacific</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-China: Two Asian Giants in an Era of Mistrust and Strategic Rivalry</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India and Europe: A Strategic Partnership Searching for Substance</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-UK Relations: Beyond Colonial History to a Modern Strategic Partnership</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India-Russia: The Enduring Partnership Tested by War and Realignment</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->81.5 Crore Aadhaar Records Exposed: Inside India&#x27;s Biggest Data Breach</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->Mission 360: Inside BJP&#x27;s Push for a Two-Thirds Majority and the Battle Over India&#x27;s Constitutional Future</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India&#x27;s 5G Revolution: 400 Million Subscribers and Still Waiting for the Killer App</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->India&#x27;s EV Paradox: Rising Sales, Stalled Charging, and the ₹4 Lakh Crore Battery Import Bill</li><li class=\"text-gray-500\">• <!-- -->Ayushman Bharat: India&#x27;s ₹30,000 Crore Bet on Universal Health Coverage</li><li class=\"text-g